      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/pakistan-stock-index-may-gain-at-least-27-by-2025-end-analysts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两家经纪公司表示，随着巴基斯坦经济在国际货币基金组织的贷款项目下出现改善且货币趋于稳定，预计到明年年底巴基斯坦股市将上涨四分之一以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/pakistan-stock-index-may-gain-at-least-27-by-2025-end-analysts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 08:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
